com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution

Class SunriseMotionExecutionContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution.SunriseExecutionContainer
      • com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.execution.SunriseMotionExecutionContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommandContainer, IExecutionContainer

    public class SunriseMotionExecutionContainer
extends SunriseExecutionContainer
    An execution container for Sunrise MOTION controller commands, in other words, this execution container should be used whenever a motion is involved.
    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
